        "## 5. Estimation via Bayesian Methods\n",
        "\n",
        "_todo: code up a metropolis-hasting MCMC sampler of the posterior distribution. Take 11,000 steps and throw away the first 1,000, retaining the subsequent 10,000._"
      ],
